  "detailed_description": "<h1>Discord Community</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/c245da42457523cf1d5b85378add6767.avif?t=1727695398\" width=600 height=74 /></span><br><strong>OUTLAWZ: Headhunter</strong> is a new survival PVP looter shooter set in a world ravaged by a virus pandemic turning most of the world’s population into mindless ghouls only seeking living breathing flesh to consume and bringing human civilization to the brink of collapse. It has been 5 years since the outbreak, and your character is one of the lucky few who survived the initial outbreak. Now you have to fight over resources and for your own life with other survivors as well as flesh-hungry infected. How far will you go to survive and dominate this world?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/eb73bbba8ef9c206fe91cfa2ca669c88.avif?t=1727695398\" width=593 height=101 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/360c6e7c737e34cdeb64de1ea1c80813.poster.avif?t=1727695398\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/360c6e7c737e34cdeb64de1ea1c80813.webm?t=1727695398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/360c6e7c737e34cdeb64de1ea1c80813.mp4?t=1727695398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Amidst the desolate wilderness, teeming with savage monsters and bands of marauders ready to seize resources at the slightest hint of weakness, humanity has gathered at the Central Safe Zone. There, they unite to establish hunting parties and strive to restore peace and prosperity to this forsaken land once more.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/8df5cf3eb22f874e3e25178f9af1acc7.avif?t=1727695398\" width=593 height=101 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/bd122eb6aee6592d2fbcf4e6e01e072e.poster.avif?t=1727695398\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/bd122eb6aee6592d2fbcf4e6e01e072e.webm?t=1727695398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/bd122eb6aee6592d2fbcf4e6e01e072e.mp4?t=1727695398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You can't be friends with everyone in the world. Sometimes, you can't avoid confrontation. Find cover and fight back when encountering groups of people. It's unlikely that they will give you love instead of bullets.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/3ce4904ac6a2dbc7d244b2e93c61000d.avif?t=1727695398\" width=593 height=101 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/6bb9dbea4b8ea225340747448e7ac01a.poster.avif?t=1727695398\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/6bb9dbea4b8ea225340747448e7ac01a.webm?t=1727695398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/6bb9dbea4b8ea225340747448e7ac01a.mp4?t=1727695398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Sometimes, vengeance becomes necessary to be exacted. When encountering murderers on the map, grab the bounty and hunt them down. Then, bring their Dog Tags to the Bounty Hunter's office to claim your reward.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/13398aa6214f8fe960b98fe839710f7b.avif?t=1727695398\" width=593 height=101 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/6bf95dacc486a733002ab0af06e3b272.poster.avif?t=1727695398\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/6bf95dacc486a733002ab0af06e3b272.webm?t=1727695398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/6bf95dacc486a733002ab0af06e3b272.mp4?t=1727695398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Humanity has been ravaged by the biological warfare between humans, leading to a global population reduction of only 20%. Furthermore, with wildlife depleted, they turn to hunting humans as their preferred dish.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/a2447f8771609208c9d8f88620ad79f2.avif?t=1727695398\" width=593 height=101 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/c44ae62bf280a2d66848e8c9863dc319.poster.avif?t=1727695398\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/c44ae62bf280a2d66848e8c9863dc319.webm?t=1727695398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/c44ae62bf280a2d66848e8c9863dc319.mp4?t=1727695398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In addition to the common mutants, there are some groups that have evolved to be even more hostile. Some of them possess extraordinary leg strength, allowing them to run faster than the fastest human beings in the world. And there's another kind that has mutated significantly. They have strength greater than that of elephants and skin thicker than armored tanks.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/cb6453eb493f4d6d144d4a0631decc37.avif?t=1727695398\" width=593 height=101 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/fbe6e207fd3d8b0062ca40382cf4f2cc.poster.avif?t=1727695398\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/fbe6e207fd3d8b0062ca40382cf4f2cc.webm?t=1727695398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/fbe6e207fd3d8b0062ca40382cf4f2cc.mp4?t=1727695398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A  Treasure from heaven comes in three types: civilian, military, and Omega. They are randomly distributed throughout the map frequently. Alternatively, if you want them to be more personalized, you can find all three levels of drops both in-game and at the Market.<br><strong>Warning!!</strong>: Don't just look up at the sky. If you're not confident enough that the area has only you present.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/1988e602f09f0e31b5d74fba261550b4.avif?t=1727695398\" width=593 height=101 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/6cbd0b9da07248fa72726f4e35a37f2d.poster.avif?t=1727695398\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/6cbd0b9da07248fa72726f4e35a37f2d.webm?t=1727695398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696190/extras/6cbd0b9da07248fa72726f4e35a37f2d.mp4?t=1727695398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Over 100 clothing and gun skin styles are available. You can obtain them by completing missions from NPCs within the game or, if you prefer not to spend time, you can check out the Market on the main menu",
